Package fr.sorbonne_u.components.hem2025e3.equipments.heater.sil

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SIL_HeaterOperationI
    The class HeaterOperationI defines the common operation used by events to execute on the heater models.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExternalTemperatureSILModel
    The class ExternalTemperatureSILModel extends the model class ExternalTemperatureModel to allow the model to log its messages on the owner component logger for software-in-the-loop tests.
    HeaterElectricitySILModel
    The class HeaterElectricitySILModel defines a simulation model for the electricity consumption of the heater.
    HeaterElectricitySILModel.HeaterElectricityReport
    The class HeaterElectricityReport implements the simulation report for the HeaterElectricityModel.
    HeaterStateSILModel
    The class HeaterStateSILModel is a simple model that tracks the current state of the heater as well as it receives events triggering state changes in the heater and reemits them towards the other heater models.
    HeaterTemperatureSILModel
    The class HeaterTemperatureSILModel defines a simulation model for the temperature inside a room equipped with a heater.
    HeaterTemperatureSILModel.HeaterTemperatureReport
    The class HeaterTemperatureReport implements the simulation report for the HeaterTemperatureModel.
    Local_SIL_SimulationArchitectures
    The class Local_SIL_SimulationArchitectures defines the local software-in-the-loop simulation architectures pertaining to the heater appliance.
    RunHeaterUnitarySILSimulation
    The class RunHeaterUnitarySimulation creates a simulator for the heater and then runs a typical simulation.
